-distance heart rate monitoring is feasible using transmittance PPGI,\nallowing for new possibilities of monitoring cardiovascular function in a\nnon-contact manner.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2015 19:19:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-24"}
