(k)$\nBerry gauge fields that arise from the self-adjoint extension parameters may be\ninteresting in the context of quantum information processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2015 13:15:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-25"}
