metric, but may be either caused\nby a monopole/anti-monopole condensate, some other types of topological objects\nor a combination of these. Removing these peaks removes the area law scaling of\nthe string tension, suggesting that they are responsible for confinement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2015 13:36:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
